# ================================
# Search Endpoints
# ================================

### Global Search
GET {{Footex_HostAddress}}/api/search?query=Manchester&page=1&pageSize=10

### Advanced Search with Strategy
GET {{Footex_HostAddress}}/api/search/strategy?query=Ronaldo&strategy=Auto&page=1&pageSize=10

### Search Teams
GET {{Footex_HostAddress}}/api/search/teams?query=United&page=1&pageSize=10

### Search Players
GET {{Footex_HostAddress}}/api/search/players?query=Cristiano&page=1&pageSize=10

### Search Matches
GET {{Footex_HostAddress}}/api/search/matches?query=Premier&page=1&pageSize=10

### Search Seasons
GET {{Footex_HostAddress}}/api/search/seasons?query=2024&page=1&pageSize=10

### Search Stadiums
GET {{Footex_HostAddress}}/api/search/stadiums?query=Old Trafford&page=1&pageSize=10

### Search Coaches
GET {{Footex_HostAddress}}/api/search/coaches?query=Guardiola&page=1&pageSize=10

### Search Suggestions
GET {{Footex_HostAddress}}/api/search/suggestions?query=Man&maxSuggestions=5

###

# ================================
# Notifications Endpoints
# ================================

### Get User Notifications
GET {{Footex_HostAddress}}/api/notifications/user/user_id_here
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get Unread Notifications Count
GET {{Footex_HostAddress}}/api/notifications/user/user_id_here/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Mark Notification as Read
POST {{Footex_HostAddress}}/api/notifications/mark-as-read/notification_id_here
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Mark All Notifications as Read
POST {{Footex_HostAddress}}/api/notifications/user/user_id_here/mark-all-as-read
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

